text: Reliance Industries surged 4.5% to Rs 971.20 after consolidated net  profit rose 25.5% to Rs 9445 crore on 25.7% growth in net sales to Rs  99810 crore in Q3 December 2017 over Q3 December 2016. The result was  announced after market hours on Friday, 19 January 2018.
